    },
    {
        "content": "<p>alexcrichton <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13209#issuecomment-4329230507\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13209\">PR #13209</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I think that's due to the script hardcoding <code>+nightly</code> which isn't in-use on this builder (it's some oss-fuzz nightly snapshot). Could the <code>+nightly</code> be removed? (I realize that'd probably remove the <code>./the/script.rs</code> aspect but that seems like a minor loss)</p>\n</blockquote>",
